By":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T15:40:19.000Z","msg":"真正讀書人，為人師表<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8886ade9329be021e78735fee3d0e8f7d2f8d873","tid":539475,"uid":62487,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T15:40:26.000Z","msg":"比錯負皮<br />\n好難得有人肯講人話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"923eb7768b1c2c7052f30ba15abfb33501448900","tid":539475,"uid":167426,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T15:40:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"136f6d736c259c7981d23ed3126aa385ba60a825","tid":539475,"uid":133751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T15:42:01.000Z","msg":"撐"}]}